Package: danStat
Type: Package
Title: A package providing a graphical user interface to the data from Danmarks
    Statistik.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-08-26
Author: Andreas Keller Leth Laursen <andreas.keller@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Andreas Keller Leth Laursen <andreas.keller@gmail.com>
Description: danStat provides a graphical user interface (GUI) to the various
   statistical series from Danmarks Statistik. Specifically danStat provides
   functions to call the API provided by Danmarks Statistik, serving as a
   wrapper around various functions from `httr` and `rjstat`. The GUI is
   implemented using `shiny`, `shinydashboard`, and `ggplot`. A future version
   will implement Highcharts.
Imports: magrittr,
    httr,
    rjstat
License: MIT + file LICENCE
LazyData: TRUE
ByteCompile: Yes
